data.description: MULTIPLE OFFFERS - HIGHEST AND BEST DUE  BY SUNDAY 6pm.  Magnolia Lakes is a gated community inside of Gateway. This home offers a 3 car garage and a fenced back yard for your kids or 4-legged friends to play under the Oak tree. The chefs Kitchen was newly updated with quartz counter tops & stainless steel appliances. Refrigerator was replaced in 2020. (2) new A/C units installed 2020. Double door entry and vaulted ceilings welcomes you home. Plantation shutters throughout. Tile & Vinyl wood floors cover the downstairs with carpet upstairs & in the bedrooms. This home also comes with a outdoor spa for you to relax under the stars.  Gateway offers a community pool for all residents and Seasonal/annual golf memberships for the sport enthusiast. Come check out this home before its gone.....
